<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a> | <a href="/quiz">Quiz</a> |
        <a href="/about">About</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About This Express.js App</h1>
      <p>
        This is a simple Express.js quiz application with Node.js and EJS
        templates.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Routes are defined in <code>routes/quiz.js</code></li>
        <li>API logic is in <code>controllers/quizController.js</code></li>
        <li>Front-end script is <code>public/js/quiz.js</code></li>
        <li>Static assets are served from <code>public/</code></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Visit the <a href="/start">Start</a> page to learn how it integrates
        with OpenTDB.
      </p>
      <p>Return to quiz: <a href="/">Home</a></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
